## [NotesMaster](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/notes-master)

### Methods

|                                                                                Method                                                                                |                                       Return type                                        |                                                                                                                                             Brief description                                                                                                                                              |
|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| [getGroups()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/notes-master#getGroups())                                                                   | [Group[]](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/group)              | Returns the list of [Group](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/group) objects on the page.                                                                                                                                                                                         |
| [getImages()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/notes-master#getImages())                                                                   | [Image[]](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/image)              | Returns the list of [Image](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/image) objects on the page.                                                                                                                                                                                         |
| [getLines()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/notes-master#getLines())                                                                     | [Line[]](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/line)                | Returns the list of [Line](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/line) objects on the page.                                                                                                                                                                                           |
| [getObjectId()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/notes-master#getObjectId())                                                               | `String`                                                                                 | Gets the unique ID for the page.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
| [getPageElementById(id)](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/notes-master#getPageElementById(String))                                         | [PageElement](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/page-element)   | Returns the [PageElement](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/page-element) on the page with the given ID, or `null` if none exists.                                                                                                                                                |
| [getPageElements()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/notes-master#getPageElements())                                                       | [PageElement[]](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/page-element) | Returns the list of [PageElement](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/page-element) objects rendered on the page.                                                                                                                                                                   |
| [getPlaceholder(placeholderType)](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/notes-master#getPlaceholder(PlaceholderType))                           | [PageElement](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/page-element)   | Returns the placeholder [PageElement](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/page-element) object for a specified [PlaceholderType](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/placeholder-type) or `null` if a matching placeholder is not present.                   |
| [getPlaceholder(placeholderType, placeholderIndex)](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/notes-master#getPlaceholder(PlaceholderType,Integer)) | [PageElement](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/page-element)   | Returns the placeholder [PageElement](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/page-element) object for a specified [PlaceholderType](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/placeholder-type) and a placeholder index, or `null` if the placeholder is not present. |
| [getPlaceholders()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/notes-master#getPlaceholders())                                                       | [PageElement[]](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/page-element) | Returns the list of placeholder [PageElement](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/page-element) objects in the page.                                                                                                                                                                |
| [getShapes()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/notes-master#getShapes())                                                                   | [Shape[]](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/shape)              | Returns the list of [Shape](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/shape) objects on the page.                                                                                                                                                                                         |
| [getSheetsCharts()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/notes-master#getSheetsCharts())                                                       | [SheetsChart[]](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/sheets-chart) | Returns the list of [SheetsChart](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/sheets-chart) objects on the page.                                                                                                                                                                            |
| [getTables()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/notes-master#getTables())                                                                   | [Table[]](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/table)              | Returns the list of [Table](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/table) objects on the page.                                                                                                                                                                                         |
| [getVideos()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/notes-master#getVideos())                                                                   | [Video[]](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/video)              | Returns the list of [Video](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/video) objects on the page.                                                                                                                                                                                         |
| [getWordArts()](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/notes-master#getWordArts())                                                               | [WordArt[]](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/word-art)         | Returns the list of [WordArt](https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/slides/word-art) objects on the page.                                                                                                                                                                                    |
